Method Detail

getAllResolutions

public abstract IDeployResolution[] getAllResolutions(IDeployResolutionContext context)
Returns all deploy resolutions irrespective of the existance of parameterizers.

The method is invoked by getResolutions(IDeployResolutionContext) and hasResolutions(IDeployResolutionContext) which further filter the results based on the availability of IDeployResolutionParameterizers for the resolutions.

Parameters:
context - the deploy resolution context.
Returns:
the deploy resolutions (never null).
